name: 纳奥米·海薇
birth_place: 加拿大,安大略省,汉密尔顿
introduction: Naomi Hewer began acting in high school. Her drama teacher, Paul Richard, was a coach and mentor. Throughout high school, Naomi spent much of her time acting, stage managing, and working backstage in numerous productions at The Guelph Little Theatre. She went on to study acting at Humber College in the "Acting For Film And Television Program" in Toronto, Canada.
